oVirt hook scripts
==================

99_fix_solaris
==============

Fix Solaris network support by removing CPU model from libvirt XML.


Installation:
-------------

* Install hook script to /usr/libexec/vdsm/hooks/before_vm_start of all oVirt hosts.

*  Append custom properties with engine-config:
engine-config -s UserDefinedVMProperties=fix_solaris=^(true|false)$' --cver=3.2
engine-service restart

Usage:
------

In the VM configuration window, open the custom properites tab and add fix_solaris=true for removing of CPU model information.
